Roasted Peanuts Stand

sell peanuts to people on the highway in middle of nowhere.

What makes my idea unique is that we will sell peanuts not only to random people but on a highway for increased sales in peanuts and increased hunger.

The idea isnt brand new but what is brand new about it is to sell to the lucrative market of the highway. Our business will captilize on the part of roadway that is the most frequently traveled but the least stocked with vendors. We will be able to takeover the market of roasted peanuts by creating roasted peanut stands all over

A typically business interation would be a trucker driving down the road at 80 miles an hour and they see the peanut sign way up ahead and they pull over for fresh roasted nuts.

Another typical business interation would be a family driving on a family road trip who is very hungry because our stand is set up in the middle on nowhere on I80 and they see the sign for some peanuts and they pull over to buy.



============================================================================================================================================

Table 1 : Roasting peanuts

Attributes : Frier, kind of peanuts, hotplate to keep peanuts hot.

Table 2 : Finance of peanuts

Attributes : cost per peanut, sale price of peanuts, cost of equipment

Table 3 : Where we will be on I80

Attributes : Traffic, Ability to see, Shape of road, Speed limit

Table 4 : Employees

Attributes : Name, age, address, phone number, male or female.

Table 5 : End purchase of peanuts

Attributes : Bought peanuts Y/N, satisfied, cash or card, type of custermer.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
End user data is for the peanut sellers to anaylise and improve their business.

The goal for my business is to capatalize on the lucrative market of I80 Interstate highway in the middle of nowhere. We will do business where no one else will and reach a market thats untouched. My goal of evaluating the business is to find out which part of I80 will be most sucessfull and see if we will stay profitable.